<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">那灯光连接了东方和东方</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<h3 id="toc2"><span><a href="/scp-1513-jp">SCP-1513-JP</a> - 标准频率50Hz地区</span></h3>
<div style="text-align: left;">
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:200px;"><img src="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-1513-jp/%E9%89%84%E5%A1%94-%E7%94%A3%E6%A5%AD-%E9%80%81%E4%BF%A1-%E9%80%81%E9%9B%BB%E7%B7%9A-%E5%86%AC%E7%A9%BA-3037110.jpg" style="width:200px;" alt="鉄塔-産業-送信-送電線-冬空-3037110.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:200px;">
<p><a href="https://pixabay.com/ja/photo-3037110/" target="_blank">Standard Freqenzy: 50 Hz Range</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>第二作。写作时间刚好一周。</p>
<p>写铁塔文章的原因在于童年作者周围的环境。因为，当时家附近有中等规模的变电所，从那里输电线路向四面延伸的光景，给当时的自己留下了很深的印象…在纸上画了很多画。因此，从加入这个网站到想到这篇文章，自己心中都总想要“想写一篇关于铁塔的文章”。</p>
<p>发布SCP-1512-JP几天后，我想到在此添加“日本商用电源频率的差异”(顺便一提，我是在调查AGE发电机的存在时了解到的)。后来产生了和<a href="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/groups-of-interest-de#toc0">第25局</a> 相关联的想法，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wanazawawww" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1805350); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1805350&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Wanazawawww" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1805350)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wanazawawww" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1805350); return false;">Wanazawawww</a></span> 所做的关于GoI的推文影响很大。调查发现，由于第25站的舞台是东德，所以随着时间的推移，出现了输电铁塔和商用电源频率的差异，是一个跨越德国的GoI。<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">过程很顺利吓了一跳。</span></p>
<p>在草稿阶段得到<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mochiduki-1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3409655); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3409655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="mochiduki_1" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3409655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mochiduki-1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3409655); return false;">mochiduki_1</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/highbriku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3646960); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3646960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="highbriku" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3646960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/highbriku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3646960); return false;">highbriku</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-kasugai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3995762); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3995762&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Dr_Kasugai" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3995762)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-kasugai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3995762); return false;">Dr_Kasugai</a></span>赞的扬相当高兴（特别是mochiduki现在偶尔也会在Twitter上发布关于这篇报道的帖子。非常感谢…）。<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enishi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3721098); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3721098&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Enishi" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3721098)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enishi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3721098); return false;">Enishi</a></span>和<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/k-cal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3383689); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3383689&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="k-cal" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3383689)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/k-cal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3383689); return false;">k-cal</a></span> 指出，文章的构成相当精益求精。据说写作Keter类对象很难，很担心能不能留下来…没有被删除就放心了。</p>
<p>特别感谢: 在网站内外进行草稿审查/批评的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-kasugai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3995762); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3995762&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Dr_Kasugai" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3995762)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-kasugai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3995762); return false;">Dr_Kasugai</a></span> 、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enishi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3721098); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3721098&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Enishi" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3721098)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enishi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3721098); return false;">Enishi</a></span> 、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/highbriku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3646960); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3646960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="highbriku" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3646960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/highbriku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3646960); return false;">highbriku</a></span> 、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/k-cal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3383689); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3383689&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="k-cal" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3383689)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/k-cal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3383689); return false;">k-cal</a></span> 、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mochiduki-1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3409655); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3409655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="mochiduki_1" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3409655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mochiduki-1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3409655); return false;">mochiduki_1</a></span> 、to2to2，借此机会表示感谢。</p>
<p>2018/10/13补记: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mint-chocolate" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4106733); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4106733&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Mint chocolate" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4106733)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mint-chocolate" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4106733); return false;">Mint chocolate</a></span> 已将本文<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1513-jp" target="_blank">翻译</a> 为SCP-CN！借此机会向其表示感谢。</p>
