<div style="background: #ffffff; padding: 10px; border: 2px solid #2F4F4F; width: 95%; margin: auto;"><a href="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/scp-1626-jp"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/author:soysoy-kusagawa/1626.png" alt="1626.png" class="image" /></a>
