<p>手复神躯</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP-1514-JP</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">为了用那手修复他者的御神体</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<h3 id="toc5"><span><a href="/scp-1514-jp">SCP-1514-JP</a> - 破碎之身</span></h3>
<div style="text-align: left;">
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:200px;"><img src="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-1514-jp/photo-1452987.jpg" style="width:200px;" alt="photo-1452987.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:200px;">
<p><a href="https://pixabay.com/ja/photo-1236578/" target="_blank">The Broken Body</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>第五作。创作时间为一周又四天。<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">不是<a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%B0%E3%81%95%E3%82%8C%E3%81%97%E3%82%A8%E3%82%AF%E3%82%BE%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E3%82%A2" target="_blank">艾克佐迪亚</a>。</span></p>
<p>在SCP-INT了解到准GoI-KO「<a href="http://scp-int.wikidot.com/goi-index#toc3">地下道教徒</a>」的存在，以及1900年上半年存在的朝鲜半岛恐怖分子「<a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BE%A9%E7%83%88%E5%9B%A3" target="_blank">义烈团</a>」的一员，有了「如果恐怖分子是匿名者，重武装，会不会很有趣」这样的想法。这是SCP-1514-JP的基础。</p>
<p>之后，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3266034); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3266034&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="snoj" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3266034)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3266034); return false;">snoj</a></span>翻译了中心页-CN「<a href="/hospital-hub">医院</a>」，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/benjaminchong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3699277); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3699277&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="BenjaminChong" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3699277)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/benjaminchong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3699277); return false;">BenjaminChong</a></span>翻译了其关联Tale「<a href="/recovery-by-our-hands">手复人躯</a>」。“医院”这个中心的内容吸引了我，决定以“义烈团夺取医院的所有物进行恐怖活动的文档”为主题进行写作。</p>
<p>当初是以义烈团为主的故事，在<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tsukiyomizuku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3344274); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3344274&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Tsukiyomizuku" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3344274)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tsukiyomizuku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3344274); return false;">Tsukiyomizuku</a></span>的指正下，让IJAMEA的职员登场，在采访记录中明确了义烈团、医院、IJAMEA之间的关系，并且在Twitter上接受了<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2767088); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2767088&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Hasuma_S" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2767088)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2767088); return false;">Hasuma_S</a></span>的意见，经过对具体故事的反复调整，我投稿了第一篇JP医院报道文章。十分感谢两位。</p>
<p>SCP-CN方面广受欢迎，令我很印象深刻。以发起人<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-aral-see" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967270); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3967270&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Dr Aral See" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3967270)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-aral-see" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967270); return false;">Dr Aral See</a></span>为首，收到了很多<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/forum/t-7293093/scp-1514-jp" target="_blank">表扬</a>时的感动，至今还记得。</p>
<p>特别感谢: 在网站内外进行草稿审查/批评的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2767088); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2767088&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Hasuma_S" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2767088)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2767088); return false;">Hasuma_S</a></span> 、to2to2、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tsukiyomizuku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3344274); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3344274&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Tsukiyomizuku" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3344274)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tsukiyomizuku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3344274); return false;">Tsukiyomizuku</a></span> 、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yzkrt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3205804); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3205804&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="yzkrt" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3205804)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yzkrt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3205804); return false;">yzkrt</a></span> 借此机会表示感谢。</p>
<p>2018/09/01补记: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mint-chocolate" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4106733); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4106733&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Mint chocolate" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4106733)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mint-chocolate" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4106733); return false;">Mint chocolate</a></span> 已将本文<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1514-jp" target="_blank">翻译</a> 为SCP-CN！借此机会向其表示感谢。</p>
<p>2020/01/10补记: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-phage" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2950095); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2950095&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Agent Phage" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2950095)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-phage" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2950095); return false;">Agent Phage</a></span> 在SCP-CN上<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/project-aodake" target="_blank">写了</a>一篇与本作品交叉链接的文章。（<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3266034); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3266034&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="snoj" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3266034)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3266034); return false;">snoj</a></span>已翻译为<a href="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/project-aodake" target="_blank">日文</a>！）！借此机会向其表示感谢。</p>
