<h3 id="toc6"><span><a href="/scp-1518-jp">SCP-1518-JP</a> - 锈齿轮</span></h3>
<div style="text-align: left;">
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:200px;"><img src="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-1518-jp/FDR.jpg" style="width:200px;" alt="FDR.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:200px;">
<p><a href="https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:FDR_at_Groton_April_1900.JPG" target="_blank">The Rusted Gears</a></p>
