</div>
<p>第六作。写作时间约一个半月。这是距上部作品约一年的创作作品。</p>
<p>本文是<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kankan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2859452); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2859452&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="KanKan" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2859452)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kankan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2859452); return false;">KanKan</a></span>主办的个人竞赛[[author:kankan|KanKan的10月信仰竞赛]]参赛作品(最终排名第五)。同时，也是与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/islandsmaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5060201); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5060201&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="islandsmaster" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5060201)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/islandsmaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5060201); return false;">islandsmaster</a></span>合著的作品。原案由我负责，执笔由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/islandsmaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5060201); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5060201&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="islandsmaster" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5060201)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/islandsmaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5060201); return false;">islandsmaster</a></span>负责。</p>
<p>这篇文章的开头，是我个人的想法，“有世代信仰的宗教一族不是也很好吗?”从<a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%9F%B3%E7%94%B0%E3%82%B9%E3%82%A4" target="_blank">石田翠</a>先生的青年漫画“<a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%AC%E9%A3%9F%E5%B0%B8%E9%AC%BC" target="_blank">东京食尸鬼：re</a>”中出现的“月山家”那里得到的的灵感并扩展，最终完成了“阿奇伯德宅”及其公子“罗伊德·阿奇伯德”这一存在的雏形。最后采访记录中出现的罗伊德的台词，确实也是以这为基础构思的。</p>
<p>嘛，在联想时文章的核心已经完成了，从这里开始就是大问题了。说到底因为这个草稿中固定下来的只有“设定(阿奇伯德宅和最后的台词)”，“SCP-1518-JP是什么”“异常性是什么”“用什么样的补充描绘故事”等其他重要的地方还没有完成。最后也没有想到好主意，阿奇伯德家族草稿放置了一段时间。</p>
<p>正式开始写作是在9月上旬。<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/islandsmaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5060201); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5060201&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="islandsmaster" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5060201)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/islandsmaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5060201); return false;">islandsmaster</a></span> 在Twitter上欣然同意将来与我合著。因此，匆忙书写了上述的“围绕”阿奇伯德家“的文章”情节，我们两人决定把文章完成。Islands也同意开始代笔草稿，最终第一版在同月中旬完成。</p>
<p>在征求第一版批评后，根据Twitter、<a class="newpage" href="/discord-guideline">SCP-JP官方聊天室</a>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aisurakuto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2579233); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2579233&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="aisurakuto" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2579233)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aisurakuto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2579233); return false;">aisurakuto</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2767088); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2767088&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Hasuma_S" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2767088)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2767088); return false;">Hasuma_S</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/highbriku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3646960); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3646960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="highbriku" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3646960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/highbriku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3646960); return false;">highbriku</a></span>收到的建议，修改了异常性(最初是“将接触到东西变成铁的现实改变能力者”)和结构，重新安排了情节。之后，Islands书写了第二版，然后以SCP-1518-JP为名发布。</p>
<p>这部作品上令人惊愕的果然是Islands的执笔能力吧…。…不仅情节内容，也追加了“菲尔莫尔神父”，“曼哈顿-斯塔腾岛联合教区”等使世界观更完善的要素，另外，文章的背景设定不多说也能让读者领悟，读第一版、二版的时候不由自主地拍了下大腿……。<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">然后睡不着了…。</span></p>
<p>另外，我个人认为，这次合著颇有收获。学习Discord服务器上的批评流程也是如此，最重要的是能够知道“如果别人用自己想的情节写作，会有什么样的文体、表达和构成？”而且这一点成功了。新作品的评价提高了写作动力。<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">要是能就这样摆脱萎靡不振就好了…。</span></p>
<p>特别感谢: 在网站内外进行草稿审查/批评的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aisurakuto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2579233); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2579233&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="aisurakuto" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2579233)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aisurakuto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2579233); return false;">aisurakuto</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2767088); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2767088&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="Hasuma_S" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2767088)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2767088); return false;">Hasuma_S</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/highbriku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3646960); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3646960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="highbriku" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3646960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/highbriku" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3646960); return false;">highbriku</a></span>、to2to2、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/winston1984" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4330160); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4330160&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="winston1984" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4330160)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/winston1984" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4330160); return false;">winston1984</a></span> 借此机会表示感谢。</p>
<p>同时，对与我一起作为合著者撰写这篇文章的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/islandsmaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5060201); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5060201&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="islandsmaster" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5060201)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/islandsmaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5060201); return false;">islandsmaster</a></span> 表示深切感谢。如果你不在，这篇文章就不会完成。<strong>非常感谢！</strong></p>
<p>2019/12/27补记: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/benjaminchong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3699277); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3699277&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606218577" alt="BenjaminChong" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3699277)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/benjaminchong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3699277); return false;">BenjaminChong</a></span> 已将本文<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1518-jp" target="_blank">翻译</a> 为SCP-CN！借此机会向其表示感谢。</p>
